WEBVTT

1
00:12:25.560 --> 00:12:27.210 
我得做些研究 不过…
Well, I'd have to study it, but...

2
00:12:29.390 --> 00:12:31.850 
我以为你们很晚才会回来
I didn't expect you guys home until late.

3
00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:34.650 
- 他怎么样 - 挺乖的 准时就去睡觉了
- How's he doing? - Good, good. He went to bed on time.

4
00:12:34.650 --> 00:12:35.440 
没闹
No fuss.

5
00:12:35.450 --> 00:12:37.510 
我给他读了一段《时代广场的蟋蟀》
Read him some of Cricket in Times Square.

6
00:12:38.950 --> 00:12:40.810 
天 你们真是太好看了
God, you guys are so attractive.

7
00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:45.150 
该死 抱歉 我没忍住说出来了
Shit. Sorry, I didn't stop that from being said.

8
00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:47.120 
没关系
No, it's okay.

9
00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:48.350 
我会按完整工时付钱
I'll pay for the whole time.

10
00:12:48.350 --> 00:12:49.700 
是我们自己要早点回来的
We decided to come home early.

11
00:12:49.710 --> 00:12:52.620 
谢谢 还有来回路上的时间
Hey, thanks. And also the travel time...

